org.lukep.javavis.metrics
Class MetricMeasurement

java.lang.Object
  org.lukep.javavis.metrics.MetricMeasurement

public class MetricMeasurement
extends java.lang.Object

Represents an individual metric measurement. This class houses the result and relations that were determined by the calculation algorithm.
